<Base
  title="About Sydney Anxiety Psychology | Telehealth Psychologist Directory"
  description="What this directory is, how it works, and why we built it. An independent resource helping people in Sydney find telehealth psychologists for anxiety."
>
  <div class="main-content">
    <div class="container">

      <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <a href="/">Home</a> &rsaquo; About
      </p>

      <h1>About This Directory</h1>

      <h2>What is Sydney Anxiety Psychology?</h2>
      <p>Sydney Anxiety Psychology is an independent directory helping people in Sydney find AHPRA-registered telehealth psychologists who specialise in anxiety. It is not a clinic, a practice, or a therapy service. We help people find suitable practitioners — we don't provide clinical care.</p>

      <h2>Why we built it</h2>
      <p>Finding a telehealth psychologist for anxiety is harder than it should be. Most directories are generic, most practice websites obscure their fees, and the Medicare system is genuinely confusing. The combination of these barriers — "who do I contact?", "what will it cost?", "does telehealth even work?" — is enough to stop many people from getting support they need and are already looking for.</p>
      <p>This directory exists to remove those barriers: clear fees, honest information about telehealth, and a straightforward way to connect with a suitable practitioner.</p>

      <h2>How practitioners are listed</h2>
      <p>All psychologists listed in this directory:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Hold current AHPRA registration (which you can verify independently at <a href="https://www.ahpra.gov.au/Registration/Registers-of-Practitioners.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ahpra.gov.au</a>)</li>
        <li>Offer telehealth appointments to clients in New South Wales</li>
        <li>Specialise in or have significant experience treating anxiety presentations</li>
        <li>Have consented to being listed and have reviewed their listing for accuracy</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Listings are not paid or ranked by commercial arrangement. We do not receive a fee per booking or referral.</p>

      <h2>How to report inaccurate information</h2>
      <p>If you notice information on this directory that appears to be inaccurate — including practitioner credentials, fees, or availability — please contact us. Accuracy is a core commitment of this directory.</p>

      <h2>Professional reviewer</h2>
      <div class="reviewer-box">
        <div>
          <span class="reviewer-box__label">Professionally reviewed by</span>
          <p class="reviewer-box__meta">Monica Ma — Registered Psychologist, AHPRA Registration No. PSY0002701499. Monica reviews directory content for clinical accuracy and AHPRA compliance. You can verify her registration at <a href="https://www.ahpra.gov.au/Registration/Registers-of-Practitioners.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ahpra.gov.au</a>. Last reviewed: June 2026.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>What this directory is not</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>We are not a clinical service and cannot provide psychological advice</li>
        <li>We are not a crisis service — for urgent mental health support, contact Lifeline on 13 11 14 or Beyond Blue on 1300 22 4636</li>
        <li>We do not guarantee specific outcomes from any practitioners listed</li>
        <li>We are not affiliated with Medicare, AHPRA, or any government body</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Privacy</h2>
      <p>We collect minimal personal information and handle it in accordance with the Australian Privacy Act 1988. See our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> for details.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
